NK126(cho)002:1: // sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che'i lo rgyus gnubs kyi bka' shog chen mo bzhugs so //
NK126(cho)002:2: dus gsum bde gshegs dpal ldan ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK126(cho)002:3: 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed kyi lha tshogs la //
NK126(cho)002:4: rig 'dzin gnubs ban sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK126(cho)002:5: lus ngag yid gsum dang bas phyag btsal nas //
NK126(cho)002:6: nyams chung blo dman rnams kyi brjed byang du //
NK126(cho)002:7: rab tu phung po rgas shing rgud pa'i dus na bris pa lags //
NK126(cho)002:8: mi ngan gnubs chung sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK126(cho)002:9: skyes pa'i pha yul sgrags kyi yang rdzong na //
NK126(cho)002:10: rus dang ming du smos pa rje chen snubs kyi bu //
NK126(cho)002:11: pha ru smos pa gsal ba byang chub snubs //
NK126(cho)002:12: ma ru smos pa 'phyims mo bkra shis mtsho //
NK126(cho)002:13: pha mes dur sa sgrags kyi ri bo che //
NK126(cho)002:14: dur gyi dkyil du tsan+dana sdong po skyes //
NK126(cho)002:15: ngo mtshar skyes nas brag dmar bsam yas nas //
NK126(cho)002:16: rgya nag ha shang spyan drangs tsan dan sdong po bstan //
NK126(cho)002:17: kho yang ngo mtshar skyes nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)002:18: gsal ba byang chub snubs kyi che rgyud la //
NK126(cho)002:19: lo yi dang po shing pho byi ba'i lo //
NK126(cho)002:20: zla ba'i dang po dpyid zla ra ba la //
NK126(cho)002:21: sras kyi dam pa sprul pa'i sku gcig 'khrungs par nges //
NK126(cho)002:22: sprul pa'i sku des 'khrungs pa'i dus na yang //
NK126(cho)002:23: dar dkar khud du dril la nyi grib mtshams su snyol //
NK126(cho)002:24: dkar gsum zas dang mngar gsum sman gyi gsos //
NK126(cho)002:25: sprul pa'i sku de phyir la bzlog srid pas //
NK126(cho)002:26: sngon la tshe chog rgyal ba'i bka' rnams sgrogs //
NK126(cho)002:27: srog 'dod grub tshad gyis la tsha tsha ci mang thob //
NK126(cho)002:28: nya stong tshes brgyad la sogs dus bzhi ru //
NK126(cho)002:29: tshogs kyi 'khor lo sbyin pa rgya chen thongs //
NK126(cho)002:30: pha mas khrims la rtag tu sdom pa bsrungs //
NK126(cho)002:31: de skad gsungs nas ha shang ngo mtshar skyes //
NK126(cho)002:32: de nas lo yi dang po shing pho byi ba'i lo //
NK126(cho)002:33: zla ba'i dang po dpyid zla ra ba la //
NK126(cho)002:34: bdag nyid ma yi rum nas btsas so skad //
NK126(cho)002:35: pha mas ha shang gsungs pa bzhin du gso ba'i rim pa bgyis //
NK126(cho)002:36: lo bdun lon nas dpal gyi gzhon nu 'o bran gyi //
NK126(cho)002:37: phyag phyir 'breng nas yig rtsis byang bar bslabs //
NK126(cho)002:38: lo dgu lon nas dpal gyi bsam yas su //
NK126(cho)002:39: rgya gar yul nas ba su d+ha ra byon //
NK126(cho)002:40: rgyal po mnga' thang che bas lo gsum chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK126(cho)002:41: de nas bdag gis ba su d+ha ra la //
NK126(cho)002:42: gser srang gsum tsam phul nas lo gsum spyan sngar bsdad //
NK126(cho)002:43: dbang lung rim par rdzogs nas dam tshig khrus lung bshad //
NK126(cho)002:44: ngo mthong bcu gnyis lon nas ba su d+ha ra yul du gshegs //
NK126(cho)002:45: yul du gshegs kar bdag la 'di skad gsung //
NK126(cho)002:46: shes rab rtsal ldan pod kyi ban chung khyod //
NK126(cho)002:47: ma thogs myur du bal po'i yul du shog /
NK126(cho)002:48: ston pa'i zhabs kyis bcag pa rdo rje'i gdan //
NK126(cho)002:49: bya rgod phung po'i ri yi lho phyogs ngos //
NK126(cho)002:50: gnod 'dul rdo rje tshal gyi nags kyi gseb //
NK126(cho)002:51: 'grub khung rgyab bsnol bya ba'i brag phug na //
NK126(cho)002:52: sgra skad nyi shu rtsa gcig mthar phyin pa'i //
NK126(cho)002:53: rol bu gu h+ya de wa tsan+t+ra bya ba yod //
NK126(cho)002:54: de yi spyan sngar bu khyod btang gis gsung //
NK126(cho)002:55: de skad gsung nas bla ma bal po'i yul du gshegs //
NK126(cho)002:56: de nas ban chung bdag gis yul zhing ldum ra gser du dril //
NK126(cho)002:57: gser srang lnga bcu rtsa gcig khyed du dril //
NK126(cho)002:58: ngo mthong bcu gsum me pho byi ba'i lo la bal bor phyin //
NK126(cho)002:59: yang le shod du dpal gyi gzhon nus bskyal //
NK126(cho)002:60: de nas ba su d+ha ra'i spyan snga na //
NK126(cho)002:61: rog po med par sdug nas yod pa la //
NK126(cho)002:62: rom bu gu h+ya'i nyams la 'di ltar gda' //
NK126(cho)002:63: bal yul yang le shod na bod kyi ban chung chos byed cig /
NK126(cho)002:64: grogs po med par sdug nas 'dug pa mthong //
NK126(cho)002:65: de nas rom bu gu h+ya de wa yis //
NK126(cho)002:66: dur khrod kang ka'i tshal du byon nas ni //
NK126(cho)002:67: de na gnod sbyin gang ba bzang po bya ba yod pa la //
NK126(cho)002:68: rdzu 'phrul can gyi gnod sbyin khyod song la //
NK126(cho)002:69: yang le shod na bod kyi ban chung chos byed gcig /
NK126(cho)002:70: gser srang lnga bcur bcas nas grogs po med par yod //
NK126(cho)002:71: ban chung de yi grogs po khyod kyis gyis //
NK126(cho)002:72: de skad byas nas gnod sbyin grogs su gtang //
NK126(cho)002:73: bdag ni yang le shod na yod pa la //
NK126(cho)002:74: bdag gi drung na 'di lta bu zhig gda' //
NK126(cho)002:75: bram ze'i phru gu shin tu mdzes pa zhig /
NK126(cho)002:76: smin dkyus ring la shin tu smin ma phra //
NK126(cho)002:77: me tog 'phreng bas mdzes par mgo la brgyan //
NK126(cho)002:78: de ltar sprul nas bdag gi mdun du byung //
NK126(cho)002:79: bdag gis bzung bas me tog phreng ba de //
NK126(cho)002:80: lag tu thogs nas bdag la 'di skad smra //
NK126(cho)002:81: khyod ni sangs rgyas yang dag thugs rje can //
NK126(cho)002:82: nga ni pha med ma med da bu ste //
NK126(cho)002:83: lha srin sde brgyad kun gyis kyang //
NK126(cho)002:84: nga la dbang bskur drag sngags gtad //
NK126(cho)002:85: nga ni gnod sbyin gang ba bzang po ste //
NK126(cho)002:86: su zhig nga la mchod dang bstod byed pa //
NK126(cho)002:87: de yis nga yi nus pa thob //
NK126(cho)002:88: dad pa can gyi ban chung khyod //
NK126(cho)002:89: nga yi lus la 'ju byed pa //
NK126(cho)002:90: sngon gyi las 'phro sad pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:91: bstan pa'i bdag por khyod gyur cig /
NK126(cho)002:92: ces zer rang gi srog snying bdag la phul //
NK126(cho)002:93: spun dang grogs po bya ba khas kyang blangs //
NK126(cho)002:94: de nas bdag gis mar 'chis nas //
NK126(cho)002:95: gu ru chen po'i spyan sngar 'chis //
NK126(cho)002:96: gong gi tshig rnams brjod pa las //
NK126(cho)002:97: gu ru'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)002:98: de ni nga yis btang ba ste //
NK126(cho)002:99: ma shor zin pa las kyi 'phro //
NK126(cho)002:100: skal ldan khyod kyi grogs su gtad //
NK126(cho)002:101: gu ru'i zhal nas de skad gsung //
NK126(cho)002:102: de nas bdag gi gu ru chen po la //
NK126(cho)002:103: gu lang gser srang sum cu tham pa phul //
NK126(cho)002:104: de nas gu ru chen po yis //
NK126(cho)002:105: drag po sngags kyi rgyud dgu dang //
NK126(cho)002:106: de yi sgrub lugs mi 'dra sogs //
NK126(cho)002:107: las kyi kha tshar thams cad dang //
NK126(cho)002:108: dgos pa tshang bar ban chung bdag la gnang //
NK126(cho)002:109: de nas bdag gi bya rgod phung po'i ri la phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)002:110: rdo rje gdan nas rgyal po'i bka' byung nas //
NK126(cho)002:111: khong gi spyan sngar bdag gi mchis pa las //
NK126(cho)002:112: rgyal pos bdag la bka' tshig 'di rnams bgo //
NK126(cho)002:113: khyod ni bod kyi ban chung chos byed ste //
NK126(cho)002:114: bod kyi bka' khrims nyams pas chos byed yong mi btsun //
NK126(cho)002:115: tsoor jag rkun choms gtog mang bas drag sngags bstan //
NK126(cho)002:116: de phyir bod kyi ban chung sangs rgyas khyod //
NK126(cho)002:117: bstan pa bsrung ba'i drag sngags mang du 'chongs //
NK126(cho)002:118: zhes bka' gnang nas de la bdag gis lan btab pa //
NK126(cho)002:119: kyee rgyal pos gsungs pa de bzhin te //
NK126(cho)002:120: bod kyi bka' khrims nyams gyur na //
NK126(cho)002:121: bstan pa 'dzin skyong srung dang gsum //
NK126(cho)002:122: dam chos yongs kyi rgyab rten lags //
NK126(cho)002:123: de phyir ban chung sangs rgyas ngas //
NK126(cho)002:124: thob dka' lus srog 'di yang ma phang bar //
NK126(cho)002:125: nyams su myong ba'i lus srog spyod pa yang //
NK126(cho)002:126: dam chos bdud rtsi lta bu tshol skyong phyir //
NK126(cho)002:127: rgya dang bal po'i yul du lan bdun mchi //
NK126(cho)002:128: de bas rgyal pos bdag la 'di ltar gnang //
NK126(cho)002:129: bod yul tsam du ma grags pa'i rgyud sde nyi shu rtsa gcig gnang //
NK126(cho)002:130: de'i nang nas sgrub lugs mi mthun brgya dang nyi shu rtsa gcig byung //
NK126(cho)002:131: rgyud sde nyi shu rtsa gcig bcud phyung ba //
NK126(cho)002:132: byang chub myur thob sbas pa'i yang gces dang //
NK126(cho)002:133: gnod byed myur du sgrol smod pa'i drag sngags gnyis //
NK126(cho)002:134: drag sngags rnam gnyis gsal bar ston pa yi //
NK126(cho)002:135: rgyud kyi rgyal po zla gsang nag pa 'di //
NK126(cho)002:136: ban chung khyod la gtod kyi sems la chongs //
NK126(cho)002:137: de skad gsung nas zla gsang ma bu gnang //
NK126(cho)002:138: de nas yang ni rgyal pos 'di skad gsung //
NK126(cho)002:139: bdag gi mes po d+harma dza ya bya ba yi //
NK126(cho)002:140: thod pa yin gyi khyod kyi dngos grub rten gyis shig /
NK126(cho)002:141: de skad gsungs nas rgyal po d+harma dza yi thod pa gnang //
NK126(cho)002:142: gzhan yang rgyud sde mang po gnang ba 'di ltar lags //
NK126(cho)002:143: rgyud la rgyud kyi yan lag bco brgyad gnang //
NK126(cho)002:144: lung gi chos la lung gi mdo bdun gnang //
NK126(cho)002:145: man ngag chos la man ngag rtsa ba bzhi po gnang //
NK126(cho)002:146: de dag kha skong sngags rgyud phyi ma bdun po gnang //
NK126(cho)002:147: de ltar sngags rgyud sum cu rtsa drug gnang ba 'di ltar lags //
NK126(cho)002:148: rgyud kyi yan lag bco brgyad ni //
NK126(cho)002:149: sarba bud+d+ha sa ma gi ni tan+t+ra zhes bya ste //
NK126(cho)002:150: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor sku yi rgyud dang //
NK126(cho)002:151: zla gsang thig le gsung gi rgyud dang //
NK126(cho)002:152: gsang ba 'dus pa thugs kyi rgyud dang //
NK126(cho)002:153: glang po che rab 'bog gi rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:154: de kho na nyid gsang ba chen po'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:157: thabs kyi zhags pa'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:158: du ma snang ba'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:159: sgron ma brtsegs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:161: gcig las mang po 'phros pa'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:162: rtse gcig bsdus pa'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:163: phur pa k+ai la ya 'byung ba'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:164: ri bo brtsegs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:166: k+ai la ya bcu gnyis 'byung ba'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:167: 'jig rten 'das pa'i mdo dang bco brgyad do //
NK126(cho)002:169: gsang ba me dpung 'bar ba'i tan+t+ra dang /
NK126(cho)002:170: rdo rje bkod pa kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo dang /
NK126(cho)002:171: nam mkha' mdzod rin po che go la'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:172: dbang chen 'dus pa rta mchog rol pa'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:173: phrin las rol pa'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:174: bang mdzod bdud rtsi'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:175: rmad du byung ba byang chub sems kyi rgyud dang bdun no //
NK126(cho)002:176: man ngag gi rtsa ba bzhi la /
NK126(cho)002:177: khu byug klong dgu kun bzang rig pa mdzod kyi rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:178: byang chub sems rmad du byung ba'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:179: mi nub rgya chen nam mkha' che'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:180: chub pa rol pa shes rab stobs kyis brgyan pa'i rgyud dang bzhi'o //
NK126(cho)002:181: yan lag gi rgyud phyi ma bdun ni /
NK126(cho)002:182: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:186: ma mo bkod pa'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:187: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:188: 'bras bu stong gi rgyud dang bdun no //
NK126(cho)002:189: de ltar gsang sngags kyi rgyud mang po gnang nas 'di skad gsung /
NK126(cho)002:190: rgyal po bdag gi yab mes rgyal po dza nas da lta phan chod du /
NK126(cho)002:191: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba bka'i brgyud pa 'di //
NK126(cho)002:192: rgyud lung man ngag gsum gyi bcud bsdus nas //
NK126(cho)002:193: bod kyi ban chung khyod la gtad kyis nan tan gyis //
NK126(cho)002:194: de skad gsungs nas bka'i brgyud pa mang po gtad //
NK126(cho)002:195: de nas bdag gi rgya gar rgyal po la //
NK126(cho)002:196: rdo rje gdan du tshogs gsog bya bar zhu ba phul //
NK126(cho)002:197: rgyal pos bka' gnang tshogs bsogs zhag gsum byas pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:198: dzab grangs yid la bzlas pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:199: chos nyid sems la gsal ba'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:200: bzlas brjod ljags la byed pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:201: sgra snyan snyan la grags pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:202: lha bran smon lam 'debs pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:203: dbang po gnyid log ma lags par //
NK126(cho)002:204: nyin dkar sa la grags pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:205: lha srin ku co 'don pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:206: rgyal ba gnas nas byon pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:207: nam mkha'i dngos po mi snang bar //
NK126(cho)002:208: sna tshogs 'od dang gzhas gang tshe //
NK126(cho)002:209: dngos po gser gyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa //
NK126(cho)002:210: bdag gi khru gang tsam du nye bar byung //
NK126(cho)002:211: dngos po ma zin bar du mi zin te //
NK126(cho)002:212: tha ma de shor tsam zhig mtheb srin bar du chags //
NK126(cho)002:213: phyag na rdo rje lta bur dngos kyi skur gyur pa //
NK126(cho)002:214: bdag la dbang bsgyur mtshan yang 'di skad brtags //
NK126(cho)002:215: don dam nges rtogs shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK126(cho)002:216: kun gyi don mkhyen mi rtog sa le mkhyen //
NK126(cho)002:217: sku la mun khang sgron me lta bur gsan phyir sangs rgyas ye shes su brtags //
NK126(cho)002:218: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med rtags su gser gyi rdo rje rtse dgu bsnams //
NK126(cho)002:219: bdag gi glo la rdo rje brtags pa 'di //
NK126(cho)002:220: tshul 'chos dpa' lo lta bu ma lags te //
NK126(cho)002:221: mi 'gyur mi shig nges pa'i lam la slob //
NK126(cho)002:222: kun rdzob rtags kyi phyag rgya 'di bzung bas //
NK126(cho)002:223: yang dag lam la bdag nyid goms par byas //
NK126(cho)002:224: bla med 'bras bu da lta nyid du thob //
NK126(cho)002:225: de nas phyag na rdo rje mthu stobs bdag po de //
NK126(cho)002:226: de skad gsungs nas gdams pa 'di skad phog /
NK126(cho)002:227: shes rab rtsal dang ldan pa'i ban chung khyod //
NK126(cho)002:228: ji tsam bar du bsdad pa'i dbang yod kyang //
NK126(cho)002:229: phyi rabs dang du len pa'i rnal 'byor rnams //
NK126(cho)002:230: 'khor ba'i chos la skyo ba skyed phyir 'da' tshul ston //
NK126(cho)002:231: phyag na rdo rje mthu stobs bdag po des //
NK126(cho)002:232: de skad dam phog 'di skad lung yang bstan //
NK126(cho)002:233: rig pa rang dbang thob pa'i ban chung sangs rgyas khyod //
NK126(cho)002:234: khyod ni don dam pha ma med pa'i sprul sku yin //
NK126(cho)002:235: sgyu ma'i phung po de nas 'od ma'i tshal du mchis //
NK126(cho)002:236: 'od ma'i tshal du yi dam bsgoms pa las //
NK126(cho)002:237: dbang po gnyid log lta bur ma lags par //
NK126(cho)002:238: ya m+aan+ta ka'i zhal mthong dngos grub gnang //
NK126(cho)002:240: gsang sngags bdag por dbang yang bskur //
NK126(cho)002:242: mkha' 'gro dbang phyug bsrung mar gtad //
NK126(cho)002:243: de nas ya m+aan+ta ka'i zhal nas 'di skad gsung //
NK126(cho)002:244: rgya gar dur khrod phug lung nag po bya ba na //
NK126(cho)002:245: spyan ras gzigs dbang thugs rje chen po yi //
NK126(cho)002:246: sprul pa 'gro ba'i don mdzad mkha' 'gro ma //
NK126(cho)002:247: sngags kyi bsrung ma e ka dza ti bya ba yod //
NK126(cho)002:248: dur khrod der song dbang dang dngos gnang gi longs //
NK126(cho)002:249: zhes gsungs nas mi snang bar gyur to //
NK126(cho)002:250: de nas bdag gis dur khrod gsang lung nag por mchis pa las //
NK126(cho)002:251: chos kyi dbyings las sprul pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK126(cho)002:252: sngags kyi bsrung ma e ka dza ti dngos dang mjal //
NK126(cho)002:253: bdag gi dngos grub rten du gyur pa'i bram ze gza' //
NK126(cho)002:254: blo gros bzang mo bya ba'i thod pa 'di //
NK126(cho)002:255: bcu gsum lon nas ming sring snol byas pa'i //
NK126(cho)002:256: snol gyi gri ru shi ba'i thod pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:257: nga yi dbang dang dngos grub 'di la yod kyi bu khyod bzung //
NK126(cho)002:258: de skad gsung nas blo gros bzang mo bram ze'i thod pa gnang //
NK126(cho)002:259: skabs der dbyings la ye shes shar nas sprul pa'i sku ru gyur //
NK126(cho)002:260: pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug bdud kyi rgyal po'i dngos kyi zhal yang mthong //
NK126(cho)002:261: dbang dang dngos grub thob pa 'di ltar gnang //
NK126(cho)002:262: 'di ni mon nag khab sra bya ba'i thod pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:263: nga yi dbang dang dngos grub 'di la yod kyi rigs kyi bu khyod bzung //
NK126(cho)002:264: de skad gsungs nas mon nag khab sra'i thod pa gnang //
NK126(cho)002:265: de nas rnam par mi rtog don la bsgom zhing mchi ba las //
NK126(cho)002:266: 'jam dpal ya m+aan+ta ka gshin rje gshed po yi //
NK126(cho)002:267: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bdag gis zhal yang mthong //
NK126(cho)002:268: dbang dang dngos grub bdag la 'di ltar gnang //
NK126(cho)002:269: yul du chos nyid gsal 'gyur gnang //
NK126(cho)002:270: don du rtogs pa rin chen gnang //
NK126(cho)002:271: grogs su rig pa'i rgyal po gnang //
NK126(cho)002:272: bu ni rang byung ye shes gnang //
NK126(cho)002:273: zla ru mnyam nyid rgyal po gnang //
NK126(cho)002:274: zas su rtog pa'i dam rdzas gnang //
NK126(cho)002:275: tshe ru 'gyur med g.yung drung gnang //
NK126(cho)002:276: bsrung ma mkha' 'gro dbang phyug gnang //
NK126(cho)002:277: mthu ru drag sngags bdun pa gnang //
NK126(cho)002:278: gnyer du slob ma 'dren pa gnang //
NK126(cho)002:279: de nas ban chung sangs rgyas bdag /
NK126(cho)002:280: ngo mtshar skyes nas lan gsum dga' //
NK126(cho)002:281: dngos grub thob nas lan gsum song //
NK126(cho)002:282: sna tshogs dka' ba'i las kyang spyod //
NK126(cho)002:283: mkhas pa mang po'i zhal yang mthong //
NK126(cho)002:284: man ngag thugs kyi bcud kyang phyin //
NK126(cho)002:285: rgyud lung kun gyi rtsa ba thob //
NK126(cho)002:286: dbang gi chu bo bzhi yang 'dus //
NK126(cho)002:287: rgyal po bka' rtags bdag la gnang //
NK126(cho)002:288: de nas ban chung bdag 'dra sangs rgyas kyis //
NK126(cho)002:289: rgya gar mkhas pa bcu gsum zhal yang mthong //
NK126(cho)002:290: sh+r+ai seng+ha'i zhal mthong bsgom sgrub man ngag gnang //
NK126(cho)002:291: ka ma shi la la sogs mkhas pa bcu bzhi yi //
NK126(cho)002:292: zhal mthong man ngag dpag med du ma gnang //
NK126(cho)002:293: de nas yang le shod du phyin pa las //
NK126(cho)002:294: slob dpon ba su d+ha ra yi //
NK126(cho)002:295: dbang bskur slob dpon mi dgos par //
NK126(cho)002:296: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud byin te //
NK126(cho)002:297: phyi yi dbang gi dbang rtags su //
NK126(cho)002:298: dam rdzas brgya dang rtsa brgyad byin //
NK126(cho)002:299: nang gi dbang gi dbang rtags su //
NK126(cho)002:300: bskur thabs lnga bcu rtsa gcig gnang //
NK126(cho)002:301: 'dren pa'i las byang che chung gtad //
NK126(cho)002:302: dbang gi bye brag don spyad nas //
NK126(cho)002:303: dbang bskur tan+t+ra'i don rdzogs nas //
NK126(cho)002:304: slob ma drongs shig lung bstan nas //
NK126(cho)002:305: dam du phog nas gnyer du gtad //
NK126(cho)002:306: de nas slar log rdo rje gdan du mchis //
NK126(cho)002:307: rgya gar rdo rje gdan drung du //
NK126(cho)002:308: gu ru chen po'i spyan sngar mchis //
NK126(cho)002:309: zhabs la spyis gtugs lha phyag 'tshal //
NK126(cho)002:310: dgyes pa rin chen sna lnga phul //
NK126(cho)002:311: gu ru'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)002:312: ha shang ma h+aa ya na rgya nag sprul pa des //
NK126(cho)002:313: dar las khyad 'phags la li dar gyi rigs //
NK126(cho)002:314: dar chen bcu gsum khyer nas rgya gar yul du byon //
NK126(cho)002:315: rgya gar rom bu gu h+ya bdag nyid la //
NK126(cho)002:316: dad pas mos nas dar yug bcu gsum phul //
NK126(cho)002:317: bdag la sprul pa'i sku des gnang ba'i dar chen bcu gsum po //
NK126(cho)002:318: bdag gi lto ru ma zos rgyab tu ma gyon par //
NK126(cho)002:319: dar la bde bar gshegs pas kha byang btab //
NK126(cho)002:320: rgya dpe bod dpe gnyis su spel nas bris //
NK126(cho)002:321: ngo mtshar can gyi dar yug bcu gsum 'di //
NK126(cho)002:322: bod kyi ban chung khyod la gtad kyi sa yi gter du sbos //
NK126(cho)002:323: de skad gsung nas dar yug bcu gsum gnang //
NK126(cho)002:324: de nas rgya gar bal yul ru mtshams su //
NK126(cho)002:325: slob dpon pad+ma rgyal po'i spyan sngar mchis //
NK126(cho)002:327: rgya gar bal yul ru mtshams kyi //
NK126(cho)002:328: rdo rje rtse lnga dgra 'dun brag phug tu //
NK126(cho)002:329: yang dag thugs kyi gter sgo phye //
NK126(cho)002:331: gsang sngags chos rnams rtsa ba ru //
NK126(cho)002:332: kun 'dus rtsa ba'i rgyud drug dang //
NK126(cho)002:333: man ngag gab pa'i gter drug dang //
NK126(cho)002:334: gsang sngags sbas pa'i 'chong drug dang //
NK126(cho)002:335: phur pa kun gyi gzhir gyur pa'i //
NK126(cho)002:336: sgrub thabs rtsa ba sde drug dang //
NK126(cho)002:337: rin chen gsang sde bco brgyad gnang //
NK126(cho)002:338: sems can mi rtag 'chi nges pas //
NK126(cho)002:339: gsang sde bco brgyad bcud phyung ba //
NK126(cho)002:340: rdzogs pa chen po'i yang snying du //
NK126(cho)002:341: gser gyi bze ru che chung dang //
NK126(cho)002:342: ye shes btsan thabs dgongs pa gnang //
NK126(cho)002:344: gsang sde bco brgyad bcud phyung ba'i //
NK126(cho)002:345: yang snying gab pa reg phung dang //
NK126(cho)002:346: rngam pa gza' yi sngags rgod ser ba'i las kha dang //
NK126(cho)002:347: lha bdun dregs chen gsang sgrub dang //
NK126(cho)002:348: mu stegs nag po'i ngan sngags bzhi //
NK126(cho)002:349: yang snying gsang sde bco brgyad dang //
NK126(cho)002:350: sngags kyi spyi dril chen po nas //
NK126(cho)002:351: yang dang yang du mdo dril nas //
NK126(cho)002:352: mngon byung lhug par bstan la phab //
NK126(cho)002:353: bsad dang gso dang dbab dang bcad //
NK126(cho)002:354: ltas ngan cho 'phrul jag chings dang //
NK126(cho)002:355: las kha bdun dang bcas pa gnang //
NK126(cho)002:356: de nas ban chung sangs rgyas dngos //
NK126(cho)002:357: da yang chos nyid don la snyems //
NK126(cho)002:358: slar log rgya gar yul du mchis //
NK126(cho)002:359: ston pa'i bzhugs gnas bkra shis byin che ba'i //
NK126(cho)002:360: bya rgod phung po'i ri yi shar gyi logs //
NK126(cho)002:361: dri zhim tsan dan tshal gyi nags kyi gseb //
NK126(cho)002:362: stag seng rgyab snol zhes bya'i brag phug tu //
NK126(cho)002:363: chos nyid don la bsgom zhing mchis pa las //
NK126(cho)002:364: bdag gi ma ru byas pa zhig /'di skad zer nas mngon du byung //
NK126(cho)002:365: bod kyi ban chung tshur son dang //
NK126(cho)002:366: nga ni kang ka'i tshal nas 'ong //
NK126(cho)002:367: sngags srung nag mo'i sprul pa ste //
NK126(cho)002:368: dur khrod gnas nas ro za ba //
NK126(cho)002:369: sprul pa bos ni ro tshol la //
NK126(cho)002:370: gtor ma chen po rtag tu thong //
NK126(cho)002:371: da rung chos nyid don ma tshol //
NK126(cho)002:372: 'gro ba sems can don la bzhugs //
NK126(cho)002:373: khyed la dngos grub ngas gter gyis //
NK126(cho)002:374: zhes mi snang bar gyur to //
NK126(cho)002:375: sngags srung de skad gsungs nas rang yul rjes su dran //
NK126(cho)002:376: slar log zla ba bcu nas gnubs yul rong du phyin //
NK126(cho)002:377: bcu bdun lon nas dam tshig rjes su dran //
NK126(cho)002:378: de nas dpal gyi gzhon nu 'o bran drung du rtol //
NK126(cho)002:379: de nas bdag gis dpal gyi gzhon nu la //
NK126(cho)002:380: dam tshig gzhung srang 'phrin las phur bu gnyis //
NK126(cho)002:381: bstan rtsigs brgya dang bcas pa gtad nas bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:382: rje yi gtad cing gnang ba'i dbyar dam zla gsang nag po 'di //
NK126(cho)002:383: dam tshig gtso ru bzung nas sa yi gter du sbas bar dgongs //
NK126(cho)002:384: de nas sngags srung bka' la nyan nas su //
NK126(cho)002:385: bod kyi rgyal khams dkar por bsgyur ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)002:386: gsang sngags bka' rnams bdag gis 'di ltar bshad //
NK126(cho)002:387: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud sde 'bum las //
NK126(cho)002:388: khyad par zab pa bstan pa gsang ba'i snying po dang //
NK126(cho)002:389: thabs kyi zhags pa sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang //
NK126(cho)002:390: he ru ka'i gal po 'jig rten 'das pa'i mdo //
NK126(cho)002:391: he ru ka 'dus tan+t+ra drug sde rgyud kyi skor //
NK126(cho)002:392: de yi sgrub thabs rnam bzhi bstan pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:393: dur khrod khu byug ye shes rngam glog dang //
NK126(cho)002:394: kun 'dus dgongs 'dus sems lung chen po lnga //
NK126(cho)002:395: rgyud lung man ngag kun gyi spyi bor bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:396: gsang sngags bslab chen bka' rgyud rgya mtsho nas //
NK126(cho)002:397: 'bum sde rgyud lung man ngag rtsa 'grel bcas //
NK126(cho)002:398: bod kyi ban chung rnams la bstan pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:399: phyi ma sgrub yig mtha' dag phyi rgyud nang rgyud nas //
NK126(cho)002:400: phan thogs che bar byas te phyi rabs kun la gtad //
NK126(cho)002:401: rgya gar mkhas pa bi ma mi tra dang //
NK126(cho)002:402: u rgyan mkhas pa pad+ma 'byung gnas dang //
NK126(cho)002:403: bal po'i mkhas pa ba su d+ha ra dang //
NK126(cho)002:404: bod kyi mkhas pa dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras //
NK126(cho)002:405: bdag la gnang ba'i man ngag 'di rnams yin //
NK126(cho)002:406: byang chub sems kyi yi ge bco brgyad po //
NK126(cho)002:407: don la dbye ba med kyang man ngag so so'i bzhed //
NK126(cho)002:408: rtsa 'brel tik+ka ces pa'i yig chung ma bu rnams //
NK126(cho)002:409: so gnubs gnyis la gtad kyi 'gro don gyis //
NK126(cho)002:410: sems can don la byed pa'i man ngag brgyad cu gnyis //
NK126(cho)002:411: mkhas pa rnam bzhi'i man ngag rgyun ma bcad //
NK126(cho)002:412: byang chub sems don man ngag ngos 'dzin byed pa'i man+t+ri ka /
NK126(cho)002:413: bu gcig yon tan rgya mtsho'i sems kyi dkyil du bstim //
NK126(cho)002:414: phyi ma nga yi rgyud la zhugs pa'i don ched du //
NK126(cho)002:415: 'phrin las kri yog gtad kyi 'gro don gyis //
NK126(cho)002:416: yo ga'i dbang phyug spyi ti phyi rabs don du bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:417: rgya gar mkhas pa'i man ngag rim par brgyud pa'i mtha' //
NK126(cho)002:418: mkhas pa rnam bzhi'i man ngag sngags lam ma chad pa //
NK126(cho)002:419: gsang sngags ma gzhir gyur pa'i sgrub yig rnam gsum po //
NK126(cho)002:420: thugs kyi sgrub pa yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid //
NK126(cho)002:421: phrin las nyid khol bsad pa'i 'chong dang bcas //
NK126(cho)002:422: skye shi med pa bdud rtsi'i sgrub lugs chen po la //
NK126(cho)002:423: 'chi med 'tshe klong tshe yi sgrub pa 'chod dang bcas //
NK126(cho)002:424: 'khor ba ru bzlog nyon mongs rtsad bcod phrin las phur pa la //
NK126(cho)002:425: bzlog 'jom phur bu gsad gsol thal phyung 'tshed dang bcas //
NK126(cho)002:426: rtsa 'brel mtshams sbyor las byang tik+ka dang //
NK126(cho)002:427: khog don mdo byang yig chung ma bur bcas //
NK126(cho)002:428: yang dag 'phrin las drag por bstan pa ni //
NK126(cho)002:429: phun sum tshogs pa'i man ngag che chung ma lus dang //
NK126(cho)002:430: rang sems bstan la 'bebs pa'i sems don 'da' kha ma //
NK126(cho)002:431: bod kyi ban chung rnams la bstan pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:432: gshin rje dmar nag rgyud dang sgrub thabs drag sngags bcas pa 'di //
NK126(cho)002:433: 'jam dpal le'u khri drug stong lus dang 'dra ba las //
NK126(cho)002:434: zla gsang nag po mgo dang 'dra ste 'khrul 'khor snying dang 'dra //
NK126(cho)002:435: gshin rje nyi ma bzhi ba mig dang 'dra ba las //
NK126(cho)002:436: zla gsang rgyud la gsum ste 'jam dpal zla gsang ni //
NK126(cho)002:437: 'gro la rtsis su byin pa'i yang gab gsang ba'i rgyud //
NK126(cho)002:438: yang gab dbang gi rgyal po bzhi /
NK126(cho)002:444: rtsis kyi yi ge drug cu rtsa gsum bcas nas bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:445: sa la pa tra kun tu bzang mo'i rgyud dang //
NK126(cho)002:446: sa la pra tra'i sgrub lugs gsum dang //
NK126(cho)002:447: sgrang lugs kyi rgyud gsum dang //
NK126(cho)002:448: thun gsum gyis bcad pa'i las su bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:449: phung byed sbas pa'i ma bzhi la /
NK126(cho)002:452: dbang gi rgyud bzhi ste bcu gnyis /
NK126(cho)002:453: sgrub lugs bdun las kyi kha tshar dang /
NK126(cho)002:455: tshar bcad pa gnyis su byas nas bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:456: ma e ka dza ti sngags kyi srung ma la /
NK126(cho)002:458: las kyi rgyud bzhi ste brgyad /
NK126(cho)002:459: ma tshang ba kha skong ba rba klong 'khyil ba'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:460: sgrub lugs rnam pa lnga ste /
NK126(cho)002:461: nag mo'i lugs su sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:462: mon mo'i lugs su sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:463: smug mo'i lugs su sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:464: ngal mo'i lugs su sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:465: srin mo'i lugs su sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:467: mi kha dog skya mo la brten nas sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:468: bam ril thod cog la brten nas sgrub pa gnyis so //
NK126(cho)002:470: nam mkha'i zu gu can gyi sgrub lugs dang /
NK126(cho)002:471: ral cig rgya mtsho'i sgrub lugs so //
NK126(cho)002:476: mon mo lcags mchu can gyi sgrub thabs dang /
NK126(cho)002:477: gser gyi sna cha can gyi sgrub lugs so //
NK126(cho)002:479: srin mo mgo 'phyang ma'i sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:480: dur khrod gnas yul ma'i sgrub lugs dang bcu'o //
NK126(cho)002:481: las kyi kha tshar nyi shu rtsa bdun dang bcas nas bzhag go //
NK126(cho)002:482: dpal lha mo'i rgyud bcu gnyis la /
NK126(cho)002:483: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i rgyud drug ste bcu gnyis so //
NK126(cho)002:484: thun mong gi rgyud brgyad de nyi shu tham pa /
NK126(cho)002:486: gnod sbyin mo'i srin mo'i lha mo'i bdud mo'i lugs su sgrub pa dang lnga'o //
NK126(cho)002:487: las kyi kha tshar brgya rtsa brgyad dang bcas nas bzhag go //
NK126(cho)002:488: shin tu 'phang bar bstan pa'i drag sngags 'di rnams yin //
NK126(cho)002:489: gsod byed dmar nag drag sngags bdun pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:490: lha mo nyo tshang drag sngags bdun pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:491: ma ma sha sha tha ma srog bcad pa'i /
NK126(cho)002:492: 'ub kyis bsdus na drag sngags bdun pa yin /
NK126(cho)002:493: gter phur las la drang ba yis tha mar rbad phata dag ni gcad pa yin /
NK126(cho)002:494: thun gyis drag sngags par phyin pa yin /
NK126(cho)002:496: sbyin sreg las kyi tshar bcad yin /
NK126(cho)002:497: rgyur sgrub mnan pa'i 'chong chung ni /
NK126(cho)002:498: mnan pa las kyi tshar gcad yin /
NK126(cho)002:499: thun dang sbyin sreg mnan pa yi /
NK126(cho)002:500: las kyi me thung gsum pa yis /
NK126(cho)002:501: shin tu zab par mnyan pas na /
NK126(cho)002:502: shin tu gzobs la dang du longs /
NK126(cho)002:503: sku bskyed dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK126(cho)002:504: las la gzud cing dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK126(cho)002:506: rbad cing sngags pas khugs nas gcod //
NK126(cho)002:507: drag po'i sbyin sreg rab tu gsang ba bdun //
NK126(cho)002:508: sbas pa bzhi yi rgyud las ni //
NK126(cho)002:509: drag sngags yin par shes par bya //
NK126(cho)002:511: hri sti drag sngags bdun pa ni //
NK126(cho)002:512: 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed kyi snying phyung nas //
NK126(cho)002:513: drag sngags bdun par shes par bya //
NK126(cho)002:514: kun gzhi rtsa ba'i drag sngags ni /
NK126(cho)002:515: gnam sa gser gyi 'bru gcig rgyud //
NK126(cho)002:516: drag sngags yin par shes par bya //
NK126(cho)002:517: bdud pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug ni //
NK126(cho)002:518: bdud kyi drag sngags yin par shes par bya //
NK126(cho)002:519: de ltar rtags te drag sngags bdun pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:521: sh+ri badz+ra drang na ma bzhi'i drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:522: ma ma sha sha drang na gsod byed drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:523: badz+ra ru ru kha nas drang na bdud kyi drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:524: de ltar bstan pa'i bstubs pa'i lag cha rnams //
NK126(cho)002:525: drag sngags bdun par the tshom med //
NK126(cho)002:526: dmigs par bya ba'i dmar nag drags sngags bdun //
NK126(cho)002:527: ya m+aan+ta ka e ka dza ti dang //
NK126(cho)002:528: kun gyi thun mong ma yin gter du sba bar dgongs //
NK126(cho)002:529: sgrub thabs sna 'ga' slad ma bu tsha'i btsas su bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:530: gnod sbyin zla gsang la sogs zla gsang gnyis //
NK126(cho)002:531: phyi ma'i rgyud la bzhag gi so sor spyad par gyis //
NK126(cho)002:532: 'khrul 'khor sdebs yig dgongs pa'i mtshon thabs lags //
NK126(cho)002:533: mdo byang che chung sgrub thabs ma bur bcas pa rnams //
NK126(cho)002:534: slang ma pu tsa'i btsas su bzhag ste gter du sbas //
NK126(cho)002:535: gshin rje'i las thabs brgyad cu rtsa gcig las //
NK126(cho)002:536: rdo rje 'jigs byed 'jigs chung ma bskyur rgya dper bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:537: slad nas mkhas pa byung na ma bzhag bsgyur bar byos //
NK126(cho)002:538: gshin rje bsad pa'i 'khor lo rab tu gsang ba'i ti ka las //
NK126(cho)002:539: dgra bo nag po bsad pa'i 'khor lo la //
NK126(cho)002:540: ya ma ra tsa bdun cu rtsa gnyis bzhag cing sbyin //
NK126(cho)002:541: gshin rje bla mtsho nag po'i rgyud las gshin rje zla gsang le'u lnga bcu rtsa gnyis pa bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:542: gshin rje 'jam dpal gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK126(cho)002:543: gshin rje nyi ma bzhi pa'i man ngag las kyi
NK126(cho)002:544: kha thun le'u phyung ste rgyud dang bcas pa bzhag
NK126(cho)002:545: /'jam dpal gshin rje nag po'i rgyud las /
NK126(cho)002:546: bsad pa'i las bcu dang bcas pa bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:547: gshin rje rtsa ba'i rgyud nag po las /
NK126(cho)002:548: gshin rje lcags kyi sbu gu bsad pa'i dug mda' phyung ste bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:549: gshin rje ga'u nag po dang /
NK126(cho)002:551: tsit+ta gsang ba'i rgyud gsum nas /
NK126(cho)002:552: gshin rje kha mthun nag po dang /
NK126(cho)002:553: phyi sgrub dang mo sgrub dang /
NK126(cho)002:554: zor mthun dang bcas te bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:555: gshin rje gtsug na me 'bar gyi rgyud nas /
NK126(cho)002:556: gshin rje kha thun nag po zhes bya ba dang /
NK126(cho)002:557: dug thun gnyis bsad pa'i las su phyung ste bzhag /'jam dpal gshin rje gshed kyi rgyud las //
NK126(cho)002:558: sku brgyan gcig pa'i sgrub thabs /
NK126(cho)002:559: srog gi 'khor lo dang bcas pa las /
NK126(cho)002:560: gshin rje gshed kyi drag sngags bdun pa dug gi zor te /
NK126(cho)002:561: chu gri mnon pa'i spe'u bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:562: gshin rje sku rgyan gcig pa ste /
NK126(cho)002:563: sku sngo skya'i dud kha ste /
NK126(cho)002:564: phyag g.yas be con g.yon sdig mdzub /
NK126(cho)002:565: dur khrod kyi brgyan gyis stibs pa /
NK126(cho)002:566: gshin rje mar la rdzis pa /
NK126(cho)002:567: drag sngags dug khrag klad khrag /
NK126(cho)002:568: dug rdzas mi'i thod par blug pa can la mngags so //
NK126(cho)002:569: gshin rje che 'bar gyi rgyud las /
NK126(cho)002:570: kha la me 'bar gyi drag sngags bzhi pa bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:571: gshin rje 'jam dpal rnon po'i rgyud las /
NK126(cho)002:572: bsad thabs 'jam dpal rnon po bsad pa'i yi ge dgu bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:573: gshin rje dmar nag spyi'i rgyud las /
NK126(cho)002:575: bsrung ba'i 'khor lo las made'u phyung ste bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:576: gshin rje nyi ma bzhi pa las /
NK126(cho)002:580: bzhi pa'i sngags steng du yang bsad pa'i las bzhi /
NK126(cho)002:581: 'gugs pa'i sngags bzhi ste bcu gnyis so //
NK126(cho)002:585: bdag po bzhi bod pa'i ste /
NK126(cho)002:586: yi dwags kyi bdag po bod pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:587: ma gdon gyi bdag po bod pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:588: 'joms byed kyi bdag po bod pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:589: za byed kyi bdag po bod pa ste /
NK126(cho)002:594: gshin rje gshed kyis bskul bar ston pa'o //
NK126(cho)002:596: 'jam dpal nag po'i thugs kyi gzer sngags ni /
NK126(cho)002:597: ga na pa ti dga' ba rgyal ba dang /
NK126(cho)002:598: stobs kyi rtsa gsum bcad pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:599: 'bru gsum gyi bsad pa bskul ba dang bcas pa'o //
NK126(cho)002:602: gying bdun sprul pa dang bcas pa la byed do //
NK126(cho)002:605: las kyi brgyan sngags ni nag po 'bru te gshin rje pho mo'i las khol du bstan pa'o //
NK126(cho)002:606: gtad pa'i las ni 'chi bdag pho mo 'bru gcig pa'i las gcig yin pa las so //
NK126(cho)002:607: gshin rje nag po rtsa rgyud phyi ma las /
NK126(cho)002:608: bsad pa'i las bcu gnyis zhes bya ste /
NK126(cho)002:609: 'khor lo rtsibs bcu gnyis pa'i las /
NK126(cho)002:610: las bcu gnyis par bsgyur nas bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:611: de la gshin rje sgrub lugs rnam pa gsum ste /
NK126(cho)002:612: phur bu la sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:616: gnas pa don gyi 'khor lo dang /
NK126(cho)002:620: de'i don shes par bya na 'phrin las kyi 'khor lo la bca' thabs don gsum ste /
NK126(cho)002:621: ro ras la bca' thabs ni /
NK126(cho)002:622: gshin rje ma tang gi sgrub lugs zhes bya'o //
NK126(cho)002:625: rim pa rkyang pa yan chod yin te /
NK126(cho)002:626: don man ngag gis shes par bya'o //
NK126(cho)002:627: gshin rje la yang rnam pa gnyis te /
NK126(cho)002:628: ye shes lnga'i gshin rje dang /
NK126(cho)002:630: ye shes kyi lha gshin rjes 'jig rten las kyi
NK126(cho)002:631: gshin rje rang dbang med par dbang du bsdus shing
NK126(cho)002:632: las la gtong ba ni gshin rje'i gshed ces bya'o
NK126(cho)002:633: // gshen rje gshed kyi gdug pa tshar gcad pa'i phyir /
NK126(cho)002:635: mo 'khor du don tshang zhing 'dus pa la bya'o //
NK126(cho)002:636: de la khro bo 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed bsnyen
NK126(cho)002:637: cing sgrub par 'dod pas a kro te ka yi
NK126(cho)002:639: ka la ru pa yi ge 'bru dgu pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:640: hri sti yi ge bcu dang gsum ni /
NK126(cho)002:641: sku gsung thugs spyi'i bsnyen pa yin /
NK126(cho)002:642: sa ma ya ni so sor bstan pa ste /
NK126(cho)002:644: bsnyen cing sgrub pa'i lha yang sum cu rtsa gnyis pa'am /
NK126(cho)002:650: 'phrin las ya ma ra dza sa t+wa me ya yi ge sum cu rtsa gnyis pa'am /
NK126(cho)002:651: bgod pa'i yi ge bcu bdun pa ste /
NK126(cho)002:652: 'khor lo bskor thabs phyi nang gsang ba dgu phrug /
NK126(cho)002:653: bzlas thabs dgongs pa mtshon bsdebs la mi bya ba'i thabs med do //
NK126(cho)002:654: gshin la 'ub kyis bsdus na drag po'i rgyud gsum ste /
NK126(cho)002:658: de la bar ba ni 'khor lo nag po'i rgyud do //
NK126(cho)002:659: dang po ni bshad pa dmar po'i rgyud do //
NK126(cho)002:660: phyi ma ni rak+sha glang mgo can gyi rgyud do //
NK126(cho)002:661: gshin rje nag po 'jigs byed zhags pa'i rgyud ni /
NK126(cho)002:662: nag po kha rgyud du blta'o //
NK126(cho)002:663: phrin las rnam bzhi bsgyur na 'phrin las bcu par blta'o //
NK126(cho)002:664: rang bsrung bar 'dod na gla mtsho nag por blta'o //
NK126(cho)002:665: sbyin sreg bya bar 'dod na zang khang du blta'o //
NK126(cho)002:666: mnan pa'i las ni 'khor lo nag po'i rgyud du blta'o //
NK126(cho)002:667: myur du bsad par 'dod na drag sngags bdun par blta'o //
NK126(cho)002:668: bskang bar 'dod na rgyu mchog rol par blta'o //
NK126(cho)002:669: kra dbab par 'dod na yo ga kra rgyud du blta'o //
NK126(cho)002:670: bam sgrub chen mo bya bar 'dod na khro bo pun+da r+ai ka'i rgyud du blta'o //
NK126(cho)002:671: sgyu sgral bar 'dod na gshin rje gsal shang gi rgyud du blta'o //
NK126(cho)002:672: 'ub kyis bsdus na ma gshin gyi sgrub pa la /
NK126(cho)002:673: ma mos ni gshin rje 'khol lo //
NK126(cho)002:674: gshin rjes ni ma mo las la 'khol lo //
NK126(cho)002:675: de'i don bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs ni /
NK126(cho)002:676: gshin rje kha thun nag po'i nyi ma bzhi pa
NK126(cho)002:677: 'khor lo thun 'debs zla ba ril po gcig tu
NK126(cho)002:679: gshin rje dmar po'i rgyud kyi sgrub thabs drag sngags ni /
NK126(cho)002:680: gshin rje dmar nag 'bar ba'i rgyud dang /
NK126(cho)002:681: gshin rje ma rgyud dmar po dang /
NK126(cho)002:682: gshin rje 'das pa'i mdo rgyud las /
NK126(cho)002:683: gshin rje lha sgrub chen mo rme phur sngags dang bcas pa bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:685: gso rgyud gsang ba yang gter dang /
NK126(cho)002:686: gshin rje se dmar srog gi sgrub pa /
NK126(cho)002:687: drag po sngags dang bcas pa bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:688: gshin rje dmar po zangs kha srog len gyi rgyud nas /
NK126(cho)002:689: ga 'u dmar nag gi gshin rje zang khang gi sgrub thabs dang /
NK126(cho)002:690: wa thod rlung dmar sngags bu bcas pa bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:691: gshin rje dmar po sngags rgyud phyi ma dang /
NK126(cho)002:692: rtsa bar bcas pa'i nang nas gshin rje dmar po srog bsad /
NK126(cho)002:694: bshan pa rgol byed dmar po'i rgyud nas /
NK126(cho)002:695: rgya'i dug mtsho che chung bsad pa'i gong du bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:696: gnod sbyin gar mkhan gyi rgyud nas /
NK126(cho)002:697: gnod sbyin khrag skyug man sngags bsad pa'i las su bkod de bzhag go //
NK126(cho)002:700: pad+ma rgyal po'i zhal snga nas /
NK126(cho)002:701: gza' sdong rgyud dang sgrub thabs bsam gyis mi khyab kyang /
NK126(cho)002:702: rtsa ba'i sngags bzhi las drangs nas srung 'khor sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:703: ma ra tsa sha las drangs nas lo ga ngan sngags su sgrub pa dang gnyis /
NK126(cho)002:704: rtsa ba'i sngags bzhi las drangs nas srung 'khor du sgrub pa la bzhi ste /
NK126(cho)002:705: rgyas pa phyi'i don du bsrung ba dang /
NK126(cho)002:706: bsdus pa nang gi don du bsrung ba dang /
NK126(cho)002:707: mdo rtsa ba'i don du bsrung ba dang /
NK126(cho)002:708: mthar thug yang snying gi don du bsrung ba dang bzhi'o //
NK126(cho)002:709: ma ra tsa sha las drangs nas /
NK126(cho)002:710: lo ga ngan sngags su sgrub pa la lnga ste
NK126(cho)002:711: hri sha las drangs nas srid pa yod kyi sgrub
NK126(cho)002:712: pa dang / na ga las drangs nas nag po lha bdun pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:713: ma ting las drangs nas 'jig rten gnas su sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:714: rak+mo las drangs nas rnal 'byor grol lam du sgrub pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:715: drag po a 'dus las drangs nas gsang ba ston
NK126(cho)002:716: lugs su sgrub pa dang lnga po las mi 'da'
NK126(cho)002:717: bar bshad do // ya ma ra tsa srog bdag ma ru rtse //
NK126(cho)002:718: 'khor gyi 'chi bdag dbang phyug chen po dang //
NK126(cho)002:719: ra hu la dang drag po lha bdun dang //
NK126(cho)002:720: lha re la ni drag sngags bdun bdun te //
NK126(cho)002:721: re re la ni yig 'bru bdun bdun no //
NK126(cho)002:722: zla gsang rgyud las drag sngags yin par shes par bya //
NK126(cho)002:723: dmar nag drag sngags mi bslu nges pa'i rgya'o //
NK126(cho)002:724: gza' bdud lha ser bcas pa'i drag sngags bdun pa ni //
NK126(cho)002:725: bsad gso dbab bcad ltas ngan cho 'phrul jag ching bdun //
NK126(cho)002:726: myur mgyogs rdzu 'phrul drag sngags phrin las te //
NK126(cho)002:727: b+hi ru dag las drangs pa'i drag sngags dang hri
NK126(cho)002:728: sha ya las drangs pa'i drag sngags bdun pa yin
NK126(cho)002:729: // lha srin sde brgyad srog gi drag sngags bdun pa ni //
NK126(cho)002:730: rtsa ba ni r+aa hu la phob las drangs pa ni //
NK126(cho)002:731: nying khu gza' yi drag sngags bdun pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:732: lo ga rlag byed drag sngags bdun pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:733: de ltar gtad pa'i drag sngags bdun pa rnams //
NK126(cho)002:734: yon tan rgya mtsho bu la gtad do rgya //
NK126(cho)002:735: bstan pa gnyan po bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK126(cho)002:736: e ka dza ti'i sngags bsrung rgyud la ni //
NK126(cho)002:737: mkhar sgrub snying thun kha thun dang //
NK126(cho)002:738: thod sgrub dug thun khrag thun cho 'phrul bdun //
NK126(cho)002:739: sgrub thabs drag sngags bdun du bcas pa ste //
NK126(cho)002:740: trag rak+sha las drangs nas ma his mtha' rten te //
NK126(cho)002:741: mkhar sgrub snying sgrub sgrub pa'i drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:742: trag rak+sha nas drang dun ting b+h+yo yi mtha' brten pa //
NK126(cho)002:743: thod pa grub pa'i drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:744: badz+ra snying gi drangs pa dug thun srog sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:745: yi ge bcu pa khrag gi srog sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:746: til du yis drang pa mo 'khrul srog sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:747: trig trig ser ser 'bar ba'i srog srog sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:748: ma ma snying kha rag gis drangs snying thun drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:749: e ka dza ti khrag thun zer na kha thun drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:750: bal tri bal tri zer na thod pa'i dug sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:751: kha se sha kha drangs na dug thun drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:752: a sa ma ya tris drangs cho 'phrul drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:753: ma ra ya thun b+h+yos drangs na khrag thun drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:754: lha mo la ni badz+ra ka ru rbad kyis drangs pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:755: de la sogs pa ming po bdun dang bcas pa yis //
NK126(cho)002:756: drag sngags bdun pa dag tu bstan pa yis //
NK126(cho)002:757: re ma ti la srog sngags 'dren lugs bzhi'am lnga las med //
NK126(cho)002:758: ma las drangs na srog gi snying po yin //
NK126(cho)002:759: ru las drangs na srog gi snying po yin //
NK126(cho)002:760: k+sha las drangs na srog gi snying po yin //
NK126(cho)002:761: trag las drangs na srog gi snying po yin //
NK126(cho)002:762: rdo rje nag mo'i rgyud nas ni /
NK126(cho)002:763: bdud mo yang ti srog gi lung 'phril gyi me long phyung ba ni //
NK126(cho)002:764: phung gsum ma yi drag sngags yin //
NK126(cho)002:765: bsad pa las kyi mtha' brtul na //
NK126(cho)002:766: las byed ma mo'i 'khor lo ni //
NK126(cho)002:767: re ma ti yi sku sgrub yin //
NK126(cho)002:768: mnan pa'i mchong chung ma bus brtul //
NK126(cho)002:769: spyir na ma mo 'di la 'khor lo lnga'am drug /
NK126(cho)002:770: e ka dza ti srid pa'i 'khor lo dang //
NK126(cho)002:771: re ma ti la srog gi 'khor lo dang //
NK126(cho)002:772: sku sgrub mnan pa'i mchong chung 'khor lo ma bu dang //
NK126(cho)002:773: lha mo nag mo 'che ba'i 'khor lo dang //
NK126(cho)002:774: gse'i lha mo bam thod ma'i 'khor lo bzhi'am lnga //
NK126(cho)002:775: zab par bstan gyi las de dang du longs //
NK126(cho)002:776: lha mo bse mo gnyis la sgrub thabs bsam mi khyab //
NK126(cho)002:777: de bzhin gying klu bdud la sogs pa bsam mi khyab //
NK126(cho)002:778: srog dang srog 'phrog srog gi sgo lcags mi shes par //
NK126(cho)002:779: drag po'i las la rgyud dang sbyor 'dod go med 'khrug pa byed pa 'dra //
NK126(cho)002:780: de bzhin bka' rgya chung chu bzhin //
NK126(cho)002:781: nyen che rab tu zab na legs //
NK126(cho)002:782: zab dgu 'di ru bkod kyi phyi rabs rnal 'byor rnams //
NK126(cho)002:783: bka' brgyud dam pa gnubs kyi rgya bo che //
NK126(cho)002:784: bstod phyir phyi rabs rnal 'byor bstan pa bsrung ba la //
NK126(cho)002:785: nyin nas nying khu brgyud de gtang ba yin //
NK126(cho)002:786: bka' brgyud 'dzin pa yin gyis phyag tu thub par gyis //
NK126(cho)002:787: de ltar bstan kyang su zhig mi nyan na //
NK126(cho)002:788: rang gi rang phung sgrub pa de la smras ci phan //
NK126(cho)002:789: de nas drug cu re gcig byi lo la //
NK126(cho)002:790: bdag gi kag la babs nas kheng log bar pa byung //
NK126(cho)002:791: sgrags su ma chags gnubs yul rong du bros //
NK126(cho)002:792: chen la zhang chung tshur ban gsum //
NK126(cho)002:793: rus gsum ban des nye nas byas //
NK126(cho)002:794: der yang ma chags snye mo bye mkhar bzung //
NK126(cho)002:795: yul khyim rdzas cha rog ban skyabs pas bsdus //
NK126(cho)002:796: nye gnas phyag tshang myang sman 'jam dpal byas //
NK126(cho)002:797: de nas bod ban bye mkhar nang na mchis pa la //
NK126(cho)002:798: kheng po'i dmag mis rtsa skor chu sgor bcug /
NK126(cho)002:799: de nas snye mo bye mkhar ri logs la //
NK126(cho)002:800: kheng po'i dmag mi gros byed mang po rnams //
NK126(cho)002:801: bod ban gsod pa'i 'dun gros byed pa mthong //
NK126(cho)002:802: bod ban mi bzhag mtha' rus skyugs pa go //
NK126(cho)002:803: de nas ban chung thugs log mkhar rtsir phyin //
NK126(cho)002:804: kheng pa gros byed thams cad tshur nyon cig /
NK126(cho)002:805: snang srid lha 'dre thams cad gzu dang dpang //
NK126(cho)002:806: bdag ni dam chos bdud rtsi lta bu mtsho skyong phyir //
NK126(cho)002:807: bcu gsum lon nas 'dzam gling khyab par khyams //
NK126(cho)002:808: rgya dang bal po'i yul du lan bdun phyin //
NK126(cho)002:809: mkhas pa rnams la zhabs tog rgyun ma chad //
NK126(cho)002:810: dam can rnams la gtor tshogs rgyun ma chad //
NK126(cho)002:811: las su chos byas don du lha gnyer nas //
NK126(cho)002:812: bdag dang gzhan gyi don du ma phye bar //
NK126(cho)002:813: 'gro ba'i don du byang chub sems bsgom nas //
NK126(cho)002:814: bros kyang ma nyan bdag gi phyir 'breng zhing //
NK126(cho)002:815: bdag la 'di 'dra'i khengs log byed pa 'di //
NK126(cho)002:816: dam chos rgya mtsho skyong ba thams cad dang //
NK126(cho)002:817: rig 'dzin lcam dral rtsal can thams cad dang //
NK126(cho)002:818: bod khams gnod sbyin mthu chen thams cad kun //
NK126(cho)002:819: ma nyes ma lan bdag la ra mda' log /
NK126(cho)002:820: ces pa brjod nas chos gos lan gsum brdabs //
NK126(cho)002:821: de skad gsung nas spyan chab gsil ba yis //
NK126(cho)002:822: rang gi dam can la sogs gong gi gzu dpang rnams //
NK126(cho)002:823: spyan chab tshar re bdag gi mdun du byon //
NK126(cho)002:824: bdag cag rnams kyi mthu rtsal 'di 'dra ste //
NK126(cho)002:825: ri bo spang gis 'degs nus rgya mtsho'i hub 'debs nus //
NK126(cho)002:826: de lta bu yi mthu dang rtsal bdog kyang //
NK126(cho)002:827: 'di ni slob dpon nyid kyi tshe rabs snga ma yi //
NK126(cho)002:828: las kyi rnam par smin pa'i tshan brdol nas //
NK126(cho)002:829: sngon chad bdag cag rnams kyis grogs ma bgyis //
NK126(cho)002:830: da ni 'jig rten rlag par bagyi'am ji ltar bgyi //
NK126(cho)002:832: de nas chos gos kyi cha nas seng ldeng gi phur pa zhig bton nas /
NK126(cho)002:833: gnod sbyin dang dam can rnams kyi srog sngags kyis btab nas dril zhing /
NK126(cho)002:834: ri pha gi ma ra ya phata /
NK126(cho)002:836: ri la me 'bar nas kheng log byed pa'i dmag
NK126(cho)002:837: dpung rnams thul gyis tshig nas lan gcig rlag bar
NK126(cho)002:838: byas so // de'i sdig sbyong gi don du bsam
NK126(cho)002:839: gtan spyan sgron nyams dang bstun nas phyi rabs kyi
NK126(cho)002:841: de nas khengs log zhi yang lo gsum bar du dbul zhing 'phongs nas /
NK126(cho)002:842: yang rdzong nang na dngos grub sgrub cing mchis pa la /
NK126(cho)002:843: lha sras mnga' thang che ba spyan drangs chos btsugs nas //
NK126(cho)002:844: bsam yas byang chub gling du chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK126(cho)002:845: slad nas yang 'brog sgang 'grim gnubs yul rong du byon //
NK126(cho)002:846: sangs rgyas bstan pa gnyan po bsrung bar bya ba dang //
NK126(cho)002:847: dkon mchog dbu 'phang bstod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)002:848: las kyis 'brel ba'i yon tan rgya mtsho dang //
NK126(cho)002:849: dad pa che ba'i legs pa'i sgron ma dang //
NK126(cho)002:850: grogs mchog dam pa ye shes dbang phyug dang //
NK126(cho)002:851: rtsol shugs gtong phod che ba'i blon rje 'phags pa bzhi //
NK126(cho)002:852: dam tshig nyams pa snying la 'jog pa 'dra nas su //
NK126(cho)002:853: dam chos gzhung bzhin bka' la brten te lo bdun bar du bshad //
NK126(cho)002:854: yon tan rgyal mtsho mang yul lan bdun btab //
NK126(cho)002:855: drag sngags chos 'di bstan par mi 'os kyang //
NK126(cho)002:856: tshangs pa'i yang gter gzhung las 'di ltar brda //
NK126(cho)002:857: skyes bu blo rtsal brtan zhing dad pa mos pa dang //
NK126(cho)002:858: lus dang srog kyang mi 'phang gtod phod na //
NK126(cho)002:859: de dang 'brel ba 'dod na drag sngags bshad //
NK126(cho)002:861: de phyir bdag gis yon tan rgya mtsho la //
NK126(cho)002:862: sgrub lugs mi mthun brgya dang rtsa bdun gtad de bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:863: bdud kyi drag sngags ser ba dbab bsrung gnyis //
NK126(cho)002:864: legs pa'i sgron ma'i btsas su bdag gis bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:865: grogs mchog dam pa ye shes dbang phyug la //
NK126(cho)002:866: lha mo nag mo mi sring sgrub pa dang //
NK126(cho)002:867: sha za nag mo'i sgrub pa gtad de bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:868: rtsol shugs gtong phod che ba'i blon rje 'phags pa la //
NK126(cho)002:869: sa la pa tra kun tu bzang mo'i sgrub pa dang //
NK126(cho)002:870: gshin rje'i drag sngags bdun pa gtad de bzhag /
NK126(cho)002:871: de yang phyi rabs dang du len pa'i bu tsha rnams kyis kyang //
NK126(cho)002:872: rang gi rigs sam rgyud las ma rtogs pa //
NK126(cho)002:873: dad pa chung zhing dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK126(cho)002:874: dam med gsang rdol byed pa'i mi nag la //
NK126(cho)002:875: don 'dir bkod pa'i man ngag lta sgom dang //
NK126(cho)002:876: sgrub dang sgrub thabs man ngag las rgyud mtha' 'dag dang //
NK126(cho)002:877: snying la gtad pa'i man ngag drag sngags mtha' dag dang //
NK126(cho)002:878: man ngag bla rdol tshig gcig bstan gyur na //
NK126(cho)002:879: 'jig rten 'di na tshe srog dbang byed pa'i //
NK126(cho)002:880: ma gshin rdo rje mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK126(cho)002:881: de la sogs pa dam can gsod byed 'khor tshogs kyis //
NK126(cho)002:882: tshe yi bar gcod myur du byas nas ni //
NK126(cho)002:883: 'jig rten phyi ma mnar med dmyal bar skye //
NK126(cho)002:884: bdag gis de skad smras pas phyi rabs mi 'jigs te //
NK126(cho)002:885: dga' rab rdo rje man chad bod 'brel pa'i //
NK126(cho)002:886: mkhas shing grub pa thob pa'i dbang dang man ngag dang //
NK126(cho)002:887: bdag la rgyun ma chad de man ngag bdag po lags //
NK126(cho)002:888: man ngag kun la byin rlabs 'tsho skyong byed pa dang //
NK126(cho)002:889: dus gsum bde gshegs chos skyong bsrung ma bdag gis mthong //
NK126(cho)002:890: kun la smras shig spel na gong ltar bka' chad 'ong //
NK126(cho)002:891: spyi don bsdus pa'i rgyud lung man ngag gsum //
NK126(cho)002:892: dka' ba nyams su blangs nas bod khams yongs la bstan //
NK126(cho)002:893: skyes bu dam pa rnams kyi sgrubs na rtags 'byung yang //
NK126(cho)002:894: nyams chung blo dman rnams kyis sangs rgyas chos la smad //
NK126(cho)002:895: da yang phyi rabs dang du len pa'i rnal 'byor rnams //
NK126(cho)002:896: bka' brgyud rtags kyi phyag rgya su 'dzin pa //
NK126(cho)002:897: man ngag dbang gi bka' rtags sho ra re //
NK126(cho)002:898: bdag gi kha chems nyon cig yon tan rgya mtsho kwa ye //
NK126(cho)002:899: khyod la gnyer gtad slob ma 'dren pa gtad //
NK126(cho)002:900: las su gtad do dbang bzhi rdzogs pa gtad //
NK126(cho)002:901: bsgom pa gtad do sgom lung sems lung gtad //
NK126(cho)002:902: sgrub pa gtad do 'jam dpal gshin rje gtad //
NK126(cho)002:903: sgrub yig mang du bu mchog khyod la gtad //
NK126(cho)002:904: mthu ru gtad do drag sngags kun rdzogs gtad //
NK126(cho)002:905: bsrung ma gtad do mkha' 'gro dbang phyug gtad //
NK126(cho)002:906: spel ba gtad do rgyud rgyal mtha' dag gtad //
NK126(cho)002:907: bdag gi kha chems gtad do yon tan rgya mtsho kwa ye //
NK126(cho)002:908: 'phreng bas lag brgyan ma byed 'dzab bsnyen rims las drongs //
NK126(cho)002:909: sgom sgrub dus las ma g.yel mchod pa rgyun du gtong //
NK126(cho)002:910: dka' ba nyams su longs la rdo rje slob dpon khur //
NK126(cho)002:911: grogs mched dam pa'i nang du dam tshig nyams par mchi'o //
NK126(cho)002:912: de la mi nyan rang rig phung du tho //
NK126(cho)002:913: de nas yang ni bod kyi ban chung la //
NK126(cho)002:914: 'od ma'i tshal nas bsgom sgrub spyod pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:915: don dam rtogs shing chos nyid gsal bar gyur pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:916: sgrub thabs nyams su blangs pas grub pa'i rtags phyung ste //
NK126(cho)002:917: nyal zhing gnyid log bsam pa med par byung ba ma yin te //
NK126(cho)002:918: dad pa brtson 'grus me ltar 'bar bar byas pa yis //
NK126(cho)002:919: gsal ba'i rtags su cho 'phrul mang po 'di ltar byung //
NK126(cho)002:920: 'jig rten lha srin mang po 'dus nas su //
NK126(cho)002:921: man ngag bdag por bdag la dbang bskur te //
NK126(cho)002:922: ye shes rang las grub pa'i mkha' 'gro mang po 'du 'du nas //
NK126(cho)002:923: bdag dang bu tsha'i rigs rgyud phyi rabs slob pa la //
NK126(cho)002:924: 'go zhing stong grogs las bya zhal gyis bzhes pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:925: de rnams kun gyis ma spel gsang sngags bka' gdams rnams //
NK126(cho)002:926: bdag rang rgyud la gter du sbas nas bzhag pa yin //
NK126(cho)002:927: de la khyod ma 'khang zhig yon tan rgya mtsho kwa ye //
NK126(cho)002:928: de nas gter du sba bar dgongs nas /
NK126(cho)002:929: bal po'i yul nas tho se li'i gzo bo bkug /
NK126(cho)002:930: bse sgrom smug po brdung zhing mchis pa la //
NK126(cho)002:931: mal gro'i yul na klu yi rgyal po des //
NK126(cho)002:932: dpag tu med pa'i 'khor dang bcas nas byon //
NK126(cho)002:933: bdag la phyag btsal gtam yang 'di skad smra //
NK126(cho)002:934: rig pa rang dbang thob pa'i slob dpon sangs rgyas khyed //
NK126(cho)002:935: mya ngan ma 'da' sems can don la bzhugs //
NK126(cho)002:936: ji tsam bar du bzhugs pa'i tshe na yang //
NK126(cho)002:937: rdzu 'phrul mthu dang nor dang bu yi dngos grub nga yis sbyin //
NK126(cho)002:939: de nas bdag gis klu yi rgyal po la //
NK126(cho)002:940: nyan pa'i glags med lan yang 'di skad btab //
NK126(cho)002:941: dgra la bsad kyis mi lang gram pa'i rdo dpung 'dra //
NK126(cho)002:942: gnyen la skyangs kyis mi 'khyong mtsho matha'i spang bu 'dra //
NK126(cho)002:943: bya ba byas bas mi zin chu yi gnyer ma 'dra //
NK126(cho)002:944: ban chung bdag gi dpe yang de 'dra ste //
NK126(cho)002:945: rdzu 'phrul mthu dang nor dang bu yi dgos pa bdag la med //
NK126(cho)002:946: ji tsam bar du bsdad pa'i dbang yod kyang //
NK126(cho)002:947: phyag na rdo rje dbang gi bka' mi cog /
NK126(cho)002:948: rgyal po bka' bzhin 'dzin pa'i bu med pas //
NK126(cho)002:949: sgyu ma'i phung po 'di dang 'grogs nas re zhig sa yi gter du sbed //
NK126(cho)002:950: bstan pa gnyan la dgos pa'i dus 'byung gi //
NK126(cho)002:951: lan gcig nga ru sdus pa zhig dang 'phrad bar shog /
NK126(cho)002:952: nga ru rdzus pa zhig dang nga yi bka' 'di 'phrad pa'i tshe //
NK126(cho)002:953: nga yi bka' 'di 'dzin dang 'chang ba dang //
NK126(cho)002:954: bka' 'di sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams la //
NK126(cho)002:955: 'jig rten klu yi nad rnams ma btang zhig /
NK126(cho)002:956: ces klu'i rgyal po la mna' bkag nas /
NK126(cho)002:957: gse sgrom ya mkhal la bdud rkos rje brang dkar gyi rgyas btab /
NK126(cho)002:958: ma 'gal la mkha' 'gro e ka dza tis rgyas btab /
NK126(cho)002:959: thams cad du sbrul gyi chun pos rgyas btab bsdam nas /
NK126(cho)002:960: klu'i rgyal po'i lto bar a tham zhes /
NK126(cho)002:961: klu'i rgyal po chen po la gtad nas bzhag go //
NK126(cho)002:962: gzhan yang snar gyi shugs pa'i gseb kyi rdo dkar po grod pu tsam gyi 'og dang /
NK126(cho)002:963: phung po ri bo che'i dpal rdo zur gsum gyi 'og dang /
NK126(cho)002:964: shangs kyi rdo rje sgrom bu dang /
NK126(cho)002:967: stag dang bya rgod 'thab pa dang /
NK126(cho)002:969: gzhan yang lho gter byang gter bzang gter ngan gter
NK126(cho)002:970: mang du phyi rabs rnams kyi btsas su sbas so
NK126(cho)002:971: // shes rab kyi nags mal tsan dan gyi lcug ma bzhi skyes /
NK126(cho)002:974: gcig gis lo ma khyer gcig gis 'bras bu khyer ro //
NK126(cho)002:975: mdor na rje sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che 'di /
NK126(cho)002:976: dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa yin pas rang
NK126(cho)002:977: don du dbang zhu mi dgos kyang gdul bya gzhan
NK126(cho)002:978: don du gang zag rgyud ma sbyang ba ltar du
NK126(cho)002:979: gnas ste / sangs rgyas gang ga'i klung gi bye
NK126(cho)002:980: ma snyed phrag bcu gnyis kyis gsang ba'i bdag po
NK126(cho)002:981: phyag na rdo rje la dbang bskur /
NK126(cho)002:982: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rjes /
NK126(cho)002:983: sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu dang /
NK126(cho)002:984: nang nus pa'i dbang lnga dang /
NK126(cho)002:985: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum la sogs pa dbang mchog bco brgyad rdzogs par bskur ro //
NK126(cho)002:986: gzhan yang u rgyan pad+ma dang /
NK126(cho)002:991: rom bu gu h+ya de wa tsan+t+ra /
NK126(cho)002:995: gnyag dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra /
NK126(cho)002:996: de ltar rgya bod kyi mkhas pa mang po'i zhal 'grim nas /
NK126(cho)002:997: mkhas pa nus pa dang ldan no //
NK126(cho)002:998: bye brag tu kun la mi ston par gsang ba bka' rtags rtsis kyi gtad rgya na gsal lo //
NK126(cho)002:999: man ngag dam pa gnubs kyi rgya po che /
NK126(cho)002:1000: gnubs lo ma rig 'byed pa'i gser thur yin //
NK126(cho)002:1001: log lta ma lus 'joms pa'i tho lum yin //
NK126(cho)002:1002: skal ldan thar par bgrod pa'i skas rtsa yin //
